{
  "text": "We have previously shown that AB\u2423C is a major tauassociated PP2A holoenzyme [CITATION_1] . The purpose of the present investigation was to provide the first comparative study of the distribution of AB\u2423C in a large number of cases from control, AD, and non-AD cases. Combined PP2A activity assays, immunohistochemical, and Western blot analyses of brain tissue were used to test the hypotheses that altered distribution of AB\u2423C contributes to the loss of PP2A activity and correlates with tangle load in AD-affected brain regions.",
